2017-10-24 (Version 1.1.0)
* Requires Ruby 2.4
* Updated prawn dependencies to latest versions.

2015-03-19 (Version 1.0.2)
* Resume#render_pdf can now accept a block and yield a Hash with page count info.

2015-03-15 (Version 1.0.1)
* Adjusted default font size

2015-03-16 (Version 1.0.0)
* Removed Vera Sans font
* Set Source Sans Pro as default font
* Added horizontal line after the header
* Requires Ruby 2.0

